how to update docker image and container
    1. remove old container
        1.1 list containers
            $ docker ps
        1.2 kill and delete container
            $ docker rm -f <silly name of container>

    2. remove image
        2.1 list images
            $ docker images
        2.2 remove image
            $ docker rmi <REPOSITORY>

    3. build image
        $ docker build -t <image name> .

    4. start container
        $ docker run -d <image name>
